{"tid":88082,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"免費學結他","createTime":"2017-01-20T10:47:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-20T17:07:35.000Z","uid":31998,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65e119a04fd6ac327b9e492187942b50cafc43ce","tid":88082,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"戴定頭盔先，由於我講明免費，所以唔涉及乜野商業野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我本身係音樂教育 degree holder，係全職 freelance musician，唔係果種掃兩下chord 就話自己識彈出黎教果種。 <br />\n<br />\n教左一段時間，發現最有 passion 學但又最冇能力學既係在職貧窮既人（即是大多數巴絲打既年紀） <br />\n所以希望可以幫到吓大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有幾個要求： <br />\n<br />\n只教四堂免費 <br />\n<br />\n時間地點要就我，近荃灣西鐵站 <br />\n<br />\n唔包括我本身既學生 <br />\n<br />\n我都係在職貧窮 JJ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 音樂人都要食飯，同埋我本身都有一堆收錢既學生。所以為左唔做爛市保障同行，我只收兩個人免費，過左果四堂後我會再收下 round ，同埋我唔公開我真正收費，呢點私下傾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢四堂只係想教到你可以有咁上下既理解能力去自學落去，for beginner 為主 <br />\n當然結果你有興趣，我好鼓勵你繼續學落去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有意請 add <a href=\"https://t.me/musicmanctc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmusicmanctc&d=w7SRCe7k2aCBnNsguPYfLHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=b5be951b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/musicmanctc</a>"},{"pid":"a7e8660048d0b71e3cc7dfd4900a0297a8737745","tid":88082,"uid":31998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T11:05:49.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ce9cd8c10f73148e87906d1e1b8352cb708e1a","tid":88082,"uid":31257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T11:08:49.000Z","msg":"想細佬試下學睇有冇興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢日日淨係識打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d48e3b32c5523398e69cf331f62496d314a8b62","tid":88082,"uid"